It also utilizes cards like Sensei's Divining Top and Manifold Key to manipulate the top of the deck and generate card advantage. The deck aims to play aggressive creatures like Nettlecyst and Glaring Fleshraker to quickly overwhelm the opponent while utilizing cards like Time Vault and The One Ring to generate extra turns and close out the game. The deck is focused on a fast-paced aggressive strategy using artifact synergy as its main engine.

The goal is to generate a large amount of mana, draw a significant number of cards, and ultimately win the game through a synergistic combination of spells and permanents.
